column4: After seeing a good friend "The Thing" got brutally killed by "Crystal Monster", He poisoned his full body and seek for revenge!

column4: Hey! The demons polluted the land!
column5: 呔！魔物污染了这片土地！

column4: You can't move anything on the dead land.
column5: 您无法移动任何死地上的东西

column4: Merge the sacred flowers of any rank to purify the land.
column5: 合并任意等级的神圣之花来净化土地

column4: Monsters will gather a lot of items for you to use or merge.
column5: 古兽会采集各种物品，方便您使用或者合成

column4: They are best at gathering sacred balls from sacred flowers.
column5: 它们最擅长从神圣之花中采集神圣之球

column4: You can purify the dead land by tapping on the Sacred Ball.
column5: 您可以通过点击神圣之球来净化死地

column4: From now on, you will get stage reward after winning a stage.
column5: 从现在起，关卡挑战成功后将会获得关卡奖励

column4: There are golds or other mysterious items in the stage reward. Sometimes even an egg can be found.
column5: 奖励通常是金币或者其他神秘的物品，有时候甚至是一颗古兽蛋！

column4: Your reward will be sent back to the home stage and put into a trophy ball.
column5: 您的奖励会被送回主场景，并装在一个战利品球中

column4: Stage reward sometime will be pick from the stage items.
column5: 关卡奖励通常会从关卡合成的物品中抽取

column4: Some of the land is so polluted that it is no longer possible to purify it by using sacred power.
column5: 有些土地被严重污染，已经无法通过神圣之力净化它

column4: Try to drag the sacred ball to connect with the dead land and merge them!
column5: 试试看，拖动神圣之球和彻底死地相连，合并他们吧！
愚蠢的人类，我们是不可战胜的！

column4: Just merge three demon statues, and I'll be free!
column5: 只要合并3个雕像，我就会被召唤出来

column4: Enemy attack! The world is polluted by them!
column5: 敌袭！！这个世界就是被它们污染的！

column4: Double tap to kill them and take back our lands!
column5: 双击杀死它们，夺回我们的土地！

column4: Ancient God is preparing some delicious wines for you.
column5: 古神正在给您准备醇香的美酒

column4: Tip: You may get mysterious items from attacking other players.
column5: 小提示：掠夺其他玩家可能获得神秘物品

column4: Tip: Merge to build higher level houses in order to shorten the rest time of Monsters.
column5: 小提示：合成更高级古兽房屋可缩短古兽休息时间

column4: Tip: Tap some items to get extra items
column5: 小提示：点击部分物品可获得额外物品

column4: Tip: There are treasures hidden in the Magical Lands.
column5: 小提示：高级地蕴藏大量珍宝

column4: Tip: Merge 5 is much effective than merge 3.
column5: 小提示：五合二比三合一更加划算哟

column4: Tip: There is a chance to find a very high quality monster in the ultimate mystery nest.
column5: 小提示：终极神秘蛋巢有几率开出极高品质的古兽哟

column4: Tip: Don't forget to claim sign-in reward every day.
column5: 小提示：别忘记每日签到

column4: Tip: You can find some very high value items in the VIP store.
column5: 小提示：VIP商店有几率出现极其珍贵的商品

column4: Tip: The higher level of a monster egg chest, the greater discount it will be.
column5: 小提示：等级越高的古兽蛋箱打折力度越大哟

column4: Tip: Get more monsters to unlock more land.
column5: 小提示：获得更多的古兽以解锁更多的土地

column4: Tip: Don't forget to update your attack team when you get more powerful monsters.
column5: 小提示：当你获得更强大的古兽时别忘记更新出战阵容

column4: Tip: Reasonable arrangement of the battle team can improve the winning rate.
column5: 小提示：合理安排出战阵容能够提高胜率哦

column4: Tip: A trophy is a symbol of honor and strength.
column5: 小提示：奖杯是荣誉与实力的象征
